data.description: Bright and Freshly painted one story family home. Large fenced yard with extra storage in the backyard and covered patio great for entertainment. Lots of parking space with additional drive way. Lots of storage space. Dedicated Laundry room with Large size washer and dryer. This house can be rented right away, NO HOA, No restrictions. Centrally located with easy access to I-75 and Turnpike. Come see it today and make this your future home.
